last_episode_to_air.name: BTS Realness
last_episode_to_air.overview: The big day is finally here, The Vivienne is ready to shoot her first music video! But when things don’t quite work out as planned, Viv receives some heavenly guidance from her idol, Cher… or at least someone who looks and sounds a lot like her – Chad Michaels.

name: The Vivienne Takes On Hollywood
overview: The Vivienne, UK's first RuPaul's Drag Race Superstar, is joined by her celebrity friends to see what it takes to make it in Hollywood.
